description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Run and jump your way to the finish line while collecting as many stars as you can to get the highest score. With 100 levels, you have a better chance to get into the high score lists. Local high scores and online high scores (requires Xbox Live Gold).
